<body onload="pageOnLoad();">


<div class="secondary">
	技能训练
</div>
<article>
	<div class="section-sep">&nbsp;</div>
	<section style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px;text-indent: 0px;">项目<span style="letter-spacing:-1px;">──</span>散客电话预订</section>
	<section style="text-indent: 0px;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">实训目的：</span>通过处理散客电话预订，掌握通过电话接受宾客订房所需的工作技能和操作步骤。</section>
	<section class="margin0" style="font-weight: bold;text-indent: 0px;">实训步骤：</section>
	<section class="indent-title">1．接听电话，问候客人（预订员礼貌礼节）。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">2．聆听客人预订要求（客人类型、抵店时间、客房类型、住店夜数、客房数量）。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">3．推销客房（酒店客房产品特点和价格、掌握销售技巧）。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">4．询问客人抵达情况。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">5．询问特殊服务。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">6．询问付款方式。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">7．复述预订内容。</section>
	<section class="indent-title margin0">8．致谢，填写客房预订单，做好资料的保存工作。</section>


	<section class="margin0" style="font-weight: bold;text-indent: 0px;">情景模拟对话：</section>
	<div class="dialogue">
	<section class="character-b" style="margin-top: 0px;"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">您好，国际酒店预订部。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">您好，我想订两个房间。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">请问您何时抵店，预计几天，同行几人？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">6 月 4 日，预住 3 天，同行 2 人。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">我们酒店有豪华套房，每间每晚 400 美元；普通套房每间每晚 350 美元；标准间每间每晚 200 美元，您想要预订那种客房？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">我想要一个普通套房就可以。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">好的。您以是什么方式付款？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">信用卡。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">好的。您是给自己订的房间吗？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">是的。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">请问该如何称呼您？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">李浩。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">电话号码？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">1999999999。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">李先生，您于 6 月 4 日乘何种交通工具，几时抵达？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">飞机，C25 次，大概下午 2:00 到达。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">好的。您还有其他要求吗？需要接机吗？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">没有了，不用。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">李先生，您将于 6 月 4 日下午 2:00 左右乘坐 C25 次航班抵达本地。预订了一个普通套间，预住 3 天，2 人同行。房费每间每晚 350 美元。您的电话是 199999999，是这样吗？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">是的。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">如果您于 6 月 4 日下午 6:00 前不能抵店，或有什么其他变化，请及时通知我们好吗？</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">好的。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #921D22;">预订员：</span><span class="character-talk">谢谢，再见。</span></section>
	<section class="character-b"><span style="color: #3a8ad8;">客人：</span><span class="character-talk">再见。</span></section>
	</div>
	 
</article>	

